graph TD
    accTitle: SNV and Indel Workflow
    accDescr: Somatic variant calling using Mutect2 and VarDict, followed by ensemble merging and full VEP / artifact annotation.

    alignment_bam[📦 **alignment** BAM] --> gatk_mutect2[⚙️ **gatk_mutect2**]
    alignment_bam --> vardict[⚙️ **vardict**]

    gatk_mutect2 --> m2_merge[⚙️ **merged** mutect2 VCF]
    vardict --> vd_merge[⚙️ **merged** vardict VCF]

    m2_merge --> ensemble_recall[⚙️ **bcbio** variation recall]
    vd_merge --> ensemble_recall

    ensemble_recall --> vt_decompose[⚙️ **vt** decompose]
    vt_decompose --> vt_normalize_1[⚙️ **vt** normalize]
    vt_normalize_1 --> vep_annotation_1[⚙️ **VEP** annotation]
    vep_annotation_1 --> artifact_annotation[⚙️ **artifact** annotation]
    artifact_annotation --> background_annotation[⚙️ **background** annotation]
    background_annotation --> hard_filter[⚙️ **somatic** hard filter]
    hard_filter --> soft_filter[⚙️ **somatic** soft filter]
    soft_filter --> somatic_vcf[📦 **final** somatic VCF]

    m2_merge --> vt_normalize_2[⚙️ **vt** normalize]
    vt_normalize_2 --> samtools_sort[⚙️ **samtools** sort]
    samtools_sort --> vep_annotation_2[⚙️ **VEP** annotation]
    vep_annotation_2 --> germline_filter[⚙️ **germline** hard filter]
    germline_filter --> bcftools_annotate[⚙️ **gnomAD** bcftools annotation]
    bcftools_annotate --> germline_vcf[📦 **germline** SNP VCF]
    
    germline_vcf -.-> cnv_module{{🔗 **CNV_SV** module}}

    classDef primary fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,stroke-width:2px,color:#1e3a5f
    classDef success fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,stroke-width:2px,color:#14532d
    classDef warm fill:#ffedd5,stroke:#ea580c,stroke-width:2px,color:#7c2d12
    classDef accent fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:2px,color:#3b0764

    class alignment_bam primary
    class somatic_vcf success
    class germline_vcf warm
    class cnv_module accent
